          <span class="badge-min">Phone number</span>
        </div>
        <div class="conclusion-text">Daviplata is phone-linked — Phone number is the core identifier. Full name appears in all non-empty flows. Document fields and Address are provider-specific (Direct PSE / pagsmile). Start with Full name + Phone number and extend based on the provider chosen.</div>
